# RoboLedger Grid Aesthetic & Functional Polish

Finalizing the UX of the transaction grid with vibrant themes and improved functional interactions.

## Proposed Changes

### [system.css](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/system.css)
- **Rainbow Theme**: Add vibrant linear gradient to Tabulator headers.
- **Typography**: Force `font-weight: 400` for cells and `600` for titles for a clean look.
- **Overflow**: Apply `max-width` and `margin: 0 auto` to prevent bleeding into viewport edges.

### [app.js](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js)
- **Header Sorting**: Enable `headerSort: true` on all columns.
- **Account Switcher**: Add "ALL" button and implement deduplication logic.
- **Typography**: Strip inline bold weights from description renderers.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- **Aesthetic**: Check for rainbow gradient in grid header.
- **Typography Check**: Ensure all text is non-bold and uniform.
- **Sorting Check**: Click every header to verify ASC/DESC/None sorting.
- **Switcher Check**: Verify "ALL" button exists and no duplicate CHQ1 pills.
